\SKT{\it nai\,s\=a tarke\,na matir\=apaney\=a prokt\=anyenaiva suj\~n\=an\=aya pre\,s\,tha,
y\=a\.m tvam\=apa\,h satyadh\,rtirbat\=asi tv\=ad\,r\.n no bh\=uy\=annaciketa\,h pra\,s\,t\=a. 9. }
\par\sitem{9.} “This wisdom is not to be had by reasoning, O beloved
