Nachiketas; only when told thee by another it brings real knowledge,—the
wisdom which thou hast gotten. Truly thou art steadfast in the Truth! Even
such a questioner as thou art may I meet with always.”
\par
\SKT{\it j\=an\=amyaha\.m \'sevadhirityanitya\.m na hyadhruvai\,h pr\=apyate hi
