\SKT{\it \=as\=ino d\=ura\.m vrajati \'say\=ano y\=ati sarvata\,h, kasta\.m mad\=amada\.m
deva\.m madanyo j\~n\=atumarhati. 21. }
\par\sitem{21.} “Seated He journeys far off, lying down He goes
everywhere. Who other than I is fit to know God, even Him who is rapture
and the transcendence of rapture?
