vibhum\=atm\=ana\.m matv\=adh\=iro na \'socati. 22. }
\par\sitem{22.} “Realising the Bodiless in bodies, the Established in things
unsettled, the Great and Omnipresent Self, the wise and steadfast soul
grieves no longer.
